DE LANQUILLETTE v. POLLOCK et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. May 14, 1894.) Action by Henry de Lanquillette against George W. Pollock and Edward Floyd Jones.

Argued before BROWN, P. J., and DYKMAN and CULLEN, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs. All concur.
